{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Ghost Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"date","date":"2018-10-01","date_pretty":"01 October, 2018","path":null,"meta_title":"Ghost Handlebars Theme Helpers: date","meta_description":"Output date formats in your Ghost publication with the date helper. More about Ghost themes inside ✨","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"handlebars","toc":null,"keywords":["api","handlebars","themes","helpers"]},"html":"<p>Usage: <code class=\"language-text\">{{date value format=&quot;formatString&quot;}}</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"description\"><a href=\"#description\" aria-label=\"description permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Description</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">{{date}}</code> is a formatting helper for outputting dates in various format. You can either pass it a date and a format string to be used to output the date like so:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"handlebars\"><pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code class=\"language-handlebars\">// outputs something like 'July 11, 2016'\n<span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">date</span> <span class=\"token variable\">published_at</span> <span class=\"token variable\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"MMMM DD, YYYY\"</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Or you can pass it a date and the timeago flag:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"handlebars\"><pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code class=\"language-handlebars\">// outputs something like '5 mins ago'\n<span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">date</span> <span class=\"token variable\">published_at</span> <span class=\"token variable\">timeago</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>If you call <code class=\"language-text\">{{date}}</code> without a format, it will default to “MMM Do, YYYY”.</p>\n<p>If you call <code class=\"language-text\">{{date}}</code> without telling it which date to display, it will default to one of two things:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>If there is a <code class=\"language-text\">published_at</code> property available (i.e. you're inside a post object) it will use that</li>\n<li>Otherwise, it will default to the current date</li>\n</ol>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">date</code> uses moment.js for formatting dates. See their documentation for a full explanation of all the different format strings that can be used.</p>\n<h3 id=\"example-code\"><a href=\"#example-code\" aria-label=\"example code permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example Code</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"handlebars\"><pre class=\"language-handlebars\"><code class=\"language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>main<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token block keyword\">#foreach</span> <span class=\"token variable\">posts</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">url</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">title</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">excerpt</span> <span class=\"token variable\">words</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"26\"</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token comment\">{{!-- Here `published_at` is set, so this will show the article date --}}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>time</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">datetime</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">date</span> <span class=\"token variable\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"YYYY-MM-DD\"</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">date</span> <span class=\"token variable\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"DD MMMM YYYY\"</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token block keyword\">/foreach</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token comment\">{{!-- Here there is no `published_at` so this will show the current year --}}</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>small<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"&copy;\">&amp;copy;</span> <span class=\"token handlebars language-handlebars\"><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">{{</span><span class=\"token variable\">date</span> <span class=\"token variable\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"YYYY\"</span><span class=\"token delimiter punctuation\">}}</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/date/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Usage: Description is a formatting helper for outputting dates in various format. You can either pass it a date and a format string to be…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/zhangh/opt/classes/website1/computervisionsite/content/api/v2/handlebars-themes/helpers/date.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/api/handlebars-themes/helpers/date/"}}